2 05:36:47','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Real Estate Consultant\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<strong>Real Estate Consultant</strong>\r\n\r\nRankProperties\'s real estate consulting services can help you turn critical and complex real estate issues into opportunities for growth. From business owners and investors to lenders and corporate groups, we offer you the experience, know-how, and the strategic planning that helps lead to better decisions. Our range of services includes: Due diligence, market studies, portfolio services, lease advisory, and more. Virtually everything you need to enhance the value of your business, you’ll find at RankProperties.\r\n\r\n•    Real Estate Due Diligence\r\n•    Real Estate Market Studies\r\n•    Portfolio Services\r\n•    Lease Advisory\r\n\r\n<strong>PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT:</strong>\r\n\r\nAt RANKPROPERTIES, we advise and manage real estate investments for our clients in various locations and across asset classes. Our real estate advisors in Chennai assists companies and high net worth individuals to manage lease, buy/sell ,develop/re-develop captive residential and commercial real estate, including large or small land parcels with a clear time-bound approach, by engaging prospective buyers / investors / developers / IPCs all on a case-to-case basis.\r\n\r\nWe manage your real estate investments as a Complete Real Estate Portfolio, linking it with your overall financial planning goals. Our real estate investment advisors can structure your assets as an income generating portfolio or an aggressive real estate portfolio for wealth creation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Objectives and Essence:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe objective of RANKPROPERTIES\'s real estate portfolio management is to ensure that the entrusted estate portfolio is managed with the best business practices and in compliance with the current legal and regulatory framework. The essence is to add value to the investment or disinvestment process with a high degree of active engagement.\r\n\r\n<strong>TRANSACTION ADVISORY SERVICES</strong>\r\n\r\nDecisions related to real estate investments need meticulous thought and robust advice. RANKPROPERTIES offers a gamut of real estate advisory services, customized to the clients\' requirements. Our expert advisors will manage your real estate investment portfolio and provide the right property advisory services. Our market research team is abreast with the evolving trends in Chennai real estate. With profound knowledge and information, we provide you with solid recommendations according to the changes in trends, to develop action plans that align with your objectives.\r\n\r\nWe offer real estate services to residential as well as institutional and commercial properties. We can suggest innovative methods of divestitures and partnerships to create diverse investment portfolios for our clients. We optimize the options available with a wide range of real estate investment opportunities that are at par with the stake holders\' expectations. We manage your assets according to your preferences and interests and ensure positive results out of them.\r\n\r\nBacked by a treasure of knowledge and experience, we provide holistic Property Advisory Services, understanding the potential of the property at hand. We have in-depth knowledge of Chennai real estate and thus, are able to provide you with accurate and strategic suggestions. Our services span over both asset acquisition and asset disposition. RANKPROPERTIES team will have a talk with you, understand your needs and then, offer you the best return on investment.\r\n\r\n<strong>a. Asset Acquisition Services</strong>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES has an excellent track record in buying and selling real estate property, despite the complicated laws of the land, governing acquisition. Our experts are at your service to simplify the tedious legal process and paper work. Our experts assist you to understand the legal jargons, technicalities and to coordinate between the seller and other stake holders to quickly close the process, thus making buying and selling property, effortless. Legal assistance to scrutinize the title deed and relevant documents to ascertain ownership and marketability are done by a panel of experts and findings shared with the buyer. Assessments pertaining to approachability, location details, status of land/building under construction etc. are reported. Another service that most clients look forward to is the scrutiny of the documents provided by the seller. Our real estate consultants go ahead and verify the authenticity of all documents pertaining to the real estate/property to identify the genuineness of the transaction. Where there is a POA (Power of Attorney), we assist the holder in executing the registration in the name of the owner. Sale deeds and agreements required for bank loans and other financial assistance are drafted and negotiations with these institutions are done by our experts at RANKPROPERTIES. The process is then taken to closure after getting the property registered in the name of the buyer. Post purchase services include transfer to documents to the current owner. Service charges are applicable on the above services. Our dedicated team of real estate legal advisors and managers are committed to demonstrate effective results. We are partnered with the best law firms that give us valuable advice relating to real estate law, which is essential part of property and project management.\r\n\r\n<strong>b.    Asset Disposition</strong>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES offers selling assistance to owners of real estate property, plots, commercial establishments and retail space. To ensure that we meet client expectations, our panel of real estate consultants and legal advisors work together seamlessly to make the sale a success. Our experts involve themselves on behalf of you, in the sale transaction, to largely safe guard your interest and to ensure smooth transition. Their tactful involvement will ensure execution of the sale deed as per the sellers’ requirements. Our real estate legal advisors then proceed to channelize their expertise to get the property registered by executing the sale deed. Our responsibility does not end with this. We ensure that your documents are procured and the registration is complete on the predetermined day. Transfer of documents in your name and other post registration activities are completed and documents handed over to you for safe keeping.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Real Estate Consultant','','publish','closed','closed','','real-estate-consultant','','','2015-12-18 10:55:43','2015-12-18 10:55:43','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=63',0,'page','',0),(64,1,'2015-12-12 05:36:47','2015-12-12 05:36:47','Contents about Real Estate Consultant','Real Estate Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','63-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 05:36:47','2015-12-12 05:36:47','',63,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/63-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(65,1,'2015-12-12 05:37:21','2015-12-12 05:37:21','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Construction Services</strong><strong>\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES is entrusted with the key activities involving translation of the physical manifestation of design, meeting all the safety and quality standards within the agreed time schedule of the project. We provide Construction Management Services for various clients in India and abroad at diverse project locations. Our services for total Construction Management of a project include:\r\n\r\nPre-construction activities such as bid management process, constructability study including   plot plan review/heavy lift study, etc\r\n\r\nConstruction activities such as\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Site construction management</li>\r\n	<li>Liaison with statutory authorities</li>\r\n	<li>Management of construction quality</li>\r\n	<li>HSE management</li>\r\n	<li>Warehouse management</li>\r\n	<li>Contracts administration</li>\r\n	<li>Pre Commissioning and commissioning assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Contract closing followed by site closing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES has wide range of expertise and experience in handling projects in petrochemicals, refineries, Cross-country pipelines, Gas processing complexes, LNG Terminals, non-ferrous metallurgy and offshore works, fertilizer, nuclear power plants, City gas distribution, Infrastructural projects, etc .\r\n\r\nHSE is an important aspect in delivery of any project that is fundamentally imbibed into our organization culture through the HSE policy. We have set up a benchmark in the field of HSE and pride ourselves in holding industry-leading record of achieving more than 80 million LTA free man hours at a stretch.\r\n\r\nOur HSE management system consists of proven specifications, standards and procedures taking into consideration the wide range of experience gained during Construction execution over the past four and half decades. HSE management includes the following:-\r\n\r\nMonitoring/ implementation of HSE Plan / JSA (Job safety analysis), erection schemes, method statements, systems Organizing HSE promotional , training, awareness programs, HSE program and meetings.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Work permit arrangement of contractors.</li>\r\n	<li>Inspection / Audits of Project sites.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinating with Owner’s HSE representative and contractors.</li>\r\n	<li>Feedback to project Mgrs of RANKPROPERTIES and Owner on HSE</li>\r\n	<li>Compilation of HSE related statistics.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinating On-site First-Aid facilities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES Construction teams on an average render supervision for more than 100 million man hours annually at sites. We have been credited with many accolades and landmarks in HSE aspects.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Construction Services','','publish','closed','closed','','construction-services','','','2015-12-24 12:35:17','2015-12-24 12:35:17','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=65',0,'page','',0),(66,1,'2015-12-12 05:37:21','2015-12-12 05:37:21','Contents about Construction Services','Construction Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','65-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 05:37:21','2015-12-12 05:37:21','',65,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/65-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2015-12-12 05:47:03','2015-12-12 05:47:03','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Welcome to Rank Properties.com\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449665881227{margin-right: 30px !important;margin-left: 30px !important;}\"]\r\n\r\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449665881227{margin-right: 30px !important;margin-left: 30px !important;}\"]\r\n\r\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"17\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"17\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"28\" css_animation=\"bottom-to-top\" style=\"vc_box_shadow\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"28\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_