nce to have modular kitchen, in the place of conventional kitchen, is due to the fact that Modular kitchen offers convenience, aesthetics and optimum space utilization. It helps the housewife in tackling the cooking chores with less work. The space management is derived through use of horizontal and vertical space. Good storage practice prevents ants, insects and cockroaches from getting into food articles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bed Room</strong>\r\n\r\nThe bedroom is that part of the house where we go to recharge and rest after a hard day’s work and the daily stress. To do so, the room must be similar to our personality to make us feel the way we should be, but it should also be designed with style, without crowding it with useless materials that would remove the idea of spacious special retreat.\r\nMany people think they know how to create a good bedroom interior design, but can they make it great? In these following pictures, there are 40 modern interior design ideas that should inspire you. Surely, some of them are a little bit exotic but you need to have something to hope for. Besides the luxurious interior design styles, you will also find some down to earth ones that you could apply to your bedroom when redesigning it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Living Room</strong>\r\n\r\n\"The Living Room you\'ve always wanted begins here! From classy sofa cum beds, sofa sets, to dining tables, we\'ve got it all. All our living room furniture is made to order. So after you pick a style that suits your lifestyle, you also get to pick from over 5 polish options and over 500 fabric samples. Need something made to a specific size? No problem!! Your stylish, made to order, hassle-free, affordable home is here. Visit any of our showrooms and come explore your options.\"\r\n\r\n<strong>False Ceiling</strong>\r\n\r\nWe at STARK INTERIO offer a wide galore of enthralling False Ceilings that enhances the beauty of your homes, offices, showrooms and corporate offices. The false ceiling enlivens the look of homes. offices &amp; showrooms. Our company creates a variety of False Ceilings such as Gypboard False Ceilings, Thermocole False Ceiling and Grid False ceiling.\r\n\r\nWe are the designers of an exquisite array of False Ceiling and Gypsum Partitions like Gypsum False Ceiling. Thermocole False Ceiling which are widely used in commercial as well as residential buildings. Their installation gives pleasing appearance to the residential and commercial building. We have a wide range of False Ceilings to make your home or office more attractive and appealing at a reasonable cost. There are many types that are accessible and can be applied to your room ceiling or office.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wall Panelling</strong>\r\n\r\nFeel like changing your interior? Need to renovate your interior? Discover Grosfillex EXAPAN panelling, a simple and decorative solution for dressing your walls. Whether your interior is contemporary, authentic, natural or tonic, the Grosfillex panelling collections cover all tastes and will adapt to all rooms in the home. Grosfillex know-how combined with the properties of PVC, make for easy installation and an impeccable, long-lasting result.\r\n<h3>Corporate Interior Design:</h3>\r\n<strong>Interior Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nOur company is one of the very well known companies in the area of interior designs. We are offering various type of interior decoration for offices. We are offering an exclusive look to the office which looks very attractive and exclusive. Our company provides top class service or different range of colors combination, textures, fabrics, furniture for the space of office interior. We are offering the interior for offices with an affordable price.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cabin Management Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nWell designed Office Cabin Management Designs represent the work culture of any organization and builds up its image in the mind of employees. We have excellence of designing the workstations, which suit the surroundings of the organization and make a great impact on the people. From conceptualization to designing and installation of all necessary furnishing items, each and every activity for developing the workstations is conducted under the close observation of experienced designers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Meeting Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nDesigning of meetingroom is a a serious challenge, as it reflects the values and status of company in front of its prospective clients. Our adept designers are well versed with the designing concepts of these rooms and undertake the interior decoration of board rooms for various popular corporate clients. Color shades of wall, ceiling &amp; floor, furnishing of lighting, blind, curtains, furniture and other decorative items, each aspect of the rooms is refurbished by our designers and given a breathtaking and professional look. While designing these rooms, we pay meticulous attention, that this designing suits the specifications and demands of our clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Conference Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nConference room is a place where employer and staff gather to appoint a meeting and hence it should be designed in a formal style which must communicate with the company image and values. Conference room requires simple aesthetic interiors coordinating with colour palate and material. This room is not for every staff member present in office arena while it is just for main heads and executives so the ambience of the room should depend on the clientele and type of business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Aluminium Composite Panel Cladding Works</strong>\r\n\r\nACP Cladding solutions offered comprise aluminum composite panel based cladding solutions that are made available with wide range of color options to choose from. Designed to provide for desired aesthetic elevation, it helps in enhancing the look of the buildings and widely find usage for meeting the demands of external cladding of buildings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotels</strong>\r\n\r\nCreating an exotic milieu in the hospitality industries, our interior designing services are availed by leading hotels and restaurants. While designing the interior of hotel lobbies, our designers keep into mind various factors such as clients\' budget, optimization of flooring space etc and furnish qualitative as well as luxurious furniture, lighting, wall decorations and other essential items, which lend them an eye catching and sumptuous look. Apart from this, we also provide interior designing consultancy services to our clients.\r\n<strong>Resorts</strong>\r\n\r\nResorts and villas are renowned for offering celebrities and wealthy globe-trotters trendy and abundant facilities for rest, recreation and fine wining &amp; dining. A lavish resort can be anything – a hill resort, beach resort, and water resort – anywhere with breathtaking views of natural scenic beauties. A lavish resort includes vast tracts of lands – sometimes as big as a whole village size – often as large as 1500-2000 acres.\r\n\r\n<strong>Restaurants</strong>\r\n\r\nThe impressive interior designing of hotels and restaurant interior design can assist them to attract large numbers of guests. We possess a deep knowledge of hotel and restaurant designing to provide maximum functionality without compromising on aesthetic looks. Our restaurant interior design services add sophistication and charm to reception room, cafe, swimming pools, bars, discotheques, entertainment zones and many other areas. While jazzing up the interior of these restaurants, we keep in mind color shades, false ceiling, flooring, lighting and other various factors.\r\n\r\n<strong>Renovation Interiors</strong>\r\nWe undertake all kinds of Renovation works that include Civil, Electrical, Plumbing, Tiling/Flooring, carpentry and Painting/polishing works. We offer designs based on elements of Vasthu and the requirements of the clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Civil</strong>: Demolition of walls, construction of new walls, extension of roof with necessary foundations, kitchen platforms etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Electrical</strong>:  New wiring, Distribution boards, switch gear, telephone wiring and networking.\r\n\r\n<strong>Plumbing</strong>:  New lines, shifting and fixing of sanitaryware and CP fittings\r\n\r\n<strong>Tiling/Flooring</strong>: In Vitrified, ceramic, glazed, Marble, Granite, Kota, Shahabad stones etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Carpentry</strong>:  Alteration and making of new doors and windows with frames, wardrobes, lofts, kitchen cabinets etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Painting</strong>:  Repainting the walls, doors, windows and grills using high quality paints and in colors that suit the ambience.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home Renovation Specialist:</strong>\r\nOur Sales staff will introduce our company to you and advice you about your options and cost. Then will send quotation for the service that you have hoped for.\r\n\r\nThird the design team will produce the architectural drawings, assists you with product selections and ensures that your requirements are met.\r\n\r\nThen we will assign a project manager to liaise between you and our entire dedicated team to make sure your renovation progresses as smoothly as possible.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Architect & Interior Design','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 13:34:48','2015-12-18 13:34:48','',168,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(263,1,'2015-12-18 13:35:31','2015-12-18 13:35:31','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]\r\n<h3><strong>Interior Architecture and Design</strong></h3>\r\nInterior spaces have the ability to generate value on a wide variety of organizational and human fronts, including productivity, health and well-being, and purchasing potential. Drawing from our broad expertise in architecture, technology and systems, branding and environments, our interior architects and designers work across geographies and sectors to create memorable and meaningful places that support operation