actise in open market to generate brokerage) nor you need to pay hefty brokerage to renew the lease\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-4 Finalize Your Home</h3>\r\n<br class=\"clearLeftRightSpace\" />After visiting the rental property let us know your selection and then we will negotiate with the landlord and get you the best possible offer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-5 Sign the Deal Form</h3>\r\n<br class=\"clearLeftRightSpace\" />In case you want something to be done on the premises like new fans, tubes, geysers or whatever you wish for, write it all down in the Deal Form. We will then speak to the landlord and intimate him about your offer. Once he agrees to the terms and conditions you pay us a token amount to block the property for you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-6 Complete Documentation</h3>\r\n<br class=\"clearLeftRightSpace\" />We will help you to complete all the Leave and License agreement and the police verification. Once the documentations are complete and you have given the rent and deposit amount, you get the keys.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-7 Move-In</h3>\r\n<br class=\"clearLeftRightSpace\" />Now you can move in your rental premises and stay happily. Always remember we are just a phone call away for any help\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Rental Property Management','','inherit','closed','closed','','307-revision-v1','','','2015-12-22 17:42:02','2015-12-22 17:42:02','',307,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/307-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(325,1,'2015-12-22 17:42:37','2015-12-22 17:42:37','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Rental property management\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_c