e.\r\n\r\nModular Kitchen is fast becoming an integral part of a home. The growing preference to have modular kitchen, in the place of conventional kitchen, is due to the fact that Modular kitchen offers convenience, aesthetics and optimum space utilization. It helps the housewife in tackling the cooking chores with less work. The space management is derived through use of horizontal and vertical space. Good storage practice prevents ants, insects and cockroaches from getting into food articles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bed Room</strong>\r\n\r\nThe bedroom is that part of the house where we go to recharge and rest after a hard day’s work and the daily stress. To do so, the room must be similar to our personality to make us feel the way we should be, but it should also be designed with style, without crowding it with useless materials that would remove the idea of spacious special retreat.\r\nMany people think they know how to create a good bedroom interior design, but can they make it great? In these following pictures, there are 40 modern interior design ideas that should inspire you. Surely, some of them are a little bit exotic but you need to have something to hope for. Besides the luxurious interior design styles, you will also find some down to earth ones that you could apply to your bedroom when redesigning it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Living Room</strong>\r\n\r\n\"The Living Room you\'ve always wanted begins here! From classy sofa cum beds, sofa sets, to dining tables, we\'ve got it all. All our living room furniture is made to order. So after you pick a style that suits your lifestyle, you also get to pick from over 5 polish options and over 500 fabric samples. Need something made to a specific size? No problem!! Your stylish, made to order, hassle-free, affordable home is here. Visit any of our showrooms and come explore your options.\"\r\n\r\n<strong>False Ceiling</strong>\r\n\r\nWe at STARK INTERIO offer a wide galore of enthralling False Ceilings that enhances the beauty of your homes, offices, showrooms and corporate offices. The false ceiling enlivens the look of homes. offices &amp; showrooms. Our company creates a variety of False Ceilings such as Gypboard False Ceilings, Thermocole False Ceiling and Grid False ceiling.\r\n\r\nWe are the designers of an exquisite array of False Ceiling and Gypsum Partitions like Gypsum False Ceiling. Thermocole False Ceiling which are widely used in commercial as well as residential buildings. Their installation gives pleasing appearance to the residential and commercial building. We have a wide range of False Ceilings to make your home or office more attractive and appealing at a reasonable cost. There are many types that are accessible and can be applied to your room ceiling or office.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wall Panelling</strong>\r\n\r\nFeel like changing your interior? Need to renovate your interior? Discover Grosfillex EXAPAN panelling, a simple and decorative solution for dressing your walls. Whether your interior is contemporary, authentic, natural or tonic, the Grosfillex panelling collections cover all tastes and will adapt to all rooms in the home. Grosfillex know-how combined with the properties of PVC, make for easy installation and an impeccable, long-lasting result.\r\n<h3>Corporate Interior Design:</h3>\r\n<strong>Interior Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nOur company is one of the very well known companies in the area of interior designs. We are offering various type of interior decoration for offices. We are offering an exclusive look to the office which looks very attractive and exclusive. Our company provides top class service or different range of colors combination, textures, fabrics, furniture for the space of office interior. We are offering the interior for offices with an affordable price.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cabin Management Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nWell designed Office Cabin Management Designs represent the work culture of any organization and builds up its image in the mind of employees. We have excellence of designing the workstations, which suit the surroundings of the organization and make a great impact on the people. From conceptualization to designing and installation of all necessary furnishing items, each and every activity for developing the workstations is conducted under the close observation of experienced designers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Meeting Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nDesigning of meetingroom is a a serious challenge, as it reflects the values and status of company in front of its prospective clients. Our adept designers are well versed with the designing concepts of these rooms and undertake the interior decoration of board rooms for various popular corporate clients. Color shades of wall, ceiling &amp; floor, furnishing of lighting, blind, curtains, furniture and other decorative items, each aspect of the rooms is refurbished by our designers and given a breathtaking and professional look. While designing these rooms, we pay meticulous attention, that this designing suits the specifications and demands of our clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Conference Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nConference room is a place where employer and staff gather to appoint a meeting and hence it should be designed in a formal style which must communicate with the company image and values. Conference room requires simple aesthetic interiors coordinating with colour palate and material. This room is not for every staff member present in office arena while it is just for main heads and executives so the ambience of the room should depend on the clientele and type of business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Aluminium Composite Panel Cladding Works</strong>\r\n\r\nACP Cladding solutions offered comprise aluminum composite panel based cladding solutions that are made available with wide range of color options to choose from. Designed to provide for desired aesthetic elevation, it helps in enhancing the look of the buildings and widely find usage for meeting the demands of external cladding of buildings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotels</strong>\r\n\r\nCreating an exotic milieu in the hospitality industries, our interior designing services are availed by leading hotels and restaurants. While designing the interior of hotel lobbies, our designers keep into mind various factors such as clients\' budget, optimization of flooring space etc and furnish qualitative as well as luxurious furniture, lighting, wall decorations and other essential items, which lend them an eye catching and sumptuous look. Apart from this, we also provide interior designing consultancy services to our clients.\r\n<strong>Resorts</strong>\r\n\r\nResorts and villas are renowned for offering celebrities and wealthy globe-trotters trendy and abundant facilities for rest, recreation and fine wining &amp; dining. A lavish resort can be anything – a hill resort, beach resort, and water resort – anywhere with breathtaking views of natural scenic beauties. A lavish resort includes vast tracts of lands – sometimes as big as a whole village size – often as large as 1500-2000 acres.\r\n\r\n<strong>Restaurants</strong>\r\n\r\nThe impressive interior designing of hotels and restaurant interior design can assist them to attract large numbers of guests. We possess a deep knowledge of hotel and restaurant designing to provide maximum functionality without compromising on aesthetic looks. Our restaurant interior design services add sophistication and charm to reception room, cafe, swimming pools, bars, discotheques, entertainment zones and many other areas. While jazzing up the interior of these restaurants, we keep in mind color shades, false ceiling, flooring, lighting and other various factors.\r\n\r\n<strong>Renovation Interiors</strong>\r\nWe undertake all kinds of Renovation works that include Civil, Electrical, Plumbing, Tiling/Flooring, carpentry and Painting/polishing works. We offer designs based on elements of Vasthu and the requirements of the clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Civil</strong>: Demolition of walls, construction of new walls, extension of roof with necessary foundations, kitchen platforms etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Electrical</strong>:  New wiring, Distribution boards, switch gear, telephone wiring and networking.\r\n\r\n<strong>Plumbing</strong>:  New lines, shifting and fixing of sanitaryware and CP fittings\r\n\r\n<strong>Tiling/Flooring</strong>: In Vitrified, ceramic, glazed, Marble, Granite, Kota, Shahabad stones etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Carpentry</strong>:  Alteration and making of new doors and windows with frames, wardrobes, lofts, kitchen cabinets etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Painting</strong>:  Repainting the walls, doors, windows and grills using high quality paints and in colors that suit the ambience.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home Renovation Specialist:</strong>\r\nOur Sales staff will introduce our company to you and advice you about your options and cost. Then will send quotation for the service that you have hoped for.\r\n\r\nThird the design team will produce the architectural drawings, assists you with product selections and ensures that your requirements are met.\r\n\r\nThen we will assign a project manager to liaise between you and our entire dedicated team to make sure your renovation progresses as smoothly as possible.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Architect & Interior Design','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-revision-v1','','','2015-12-24 12:33:35','2015-12-24 12:33:35','',168,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(364,1,'2015-12-24 12:34:27','2015-12-24 12:34:27','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Buying &amp; Selling Properties\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Residential Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have a wide experience in sale, purchase of residential properties. We have a database of various clients who want to sell or buy properties. We identify and understand the need of our clients and help them in finding a suitable property, which suits there necessity and budget. We maintain privacy about buyers/sellers and conclude the deal at the best market prices. We offer flexible and comprehensive range of services and considerable knowledge of the market place. Our experience will ensure that you are in safe hands, if you are buying and selling any residential property.\r\n<h3><strong>Commercial Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have a wide experience in sale, purchase of commercial properties. As it is know that it is the era of Commercial Malls, Cine multiplex, Amusement parks, Software parks etc. We identify and understand the need of our clients and help them in finding a suitable commercial land for establishing their business according to their budget. With our professional and dedicated team, we endeavor to make the world a better place. We intend to provide a more prosperous, safer and stable future for you business needs.\r\n<h3><strong>Agricultural Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have complete real estate representative offers complete solution for various agricultural properties. Our knowledge, experience and manpower had resulted in some of the big agricultural property dealing in U.P, Delhi and NCR. The property demand in this location is increasing day by day due to its nearness to the national capital. If you want to earn profit try to invest in these prime areas. Our experts have calculated that property rate is increasing rapidly and investing in agriculture land is very sound idea. So if you want to know more about the property land, locations, prices feel free to contact us at any time. Our experts will entertain your queries to resolve all issues.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Buying & Selling Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','161-revision-v1','','','2015-12-24 12:34:27','2015-12-24 12:34:27','',161,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/161-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(365,1,'2015-12-24 12:34:45','2015-12-24 12:34:45','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Buying Properties\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]In Andhra Pradesh we are well-known real estate consultancy. Our team supports the clients to making property investments in any locations in Andhra Pradesh. We are having property database in huge numbers. You just give us your complete information about the requirement like what kind of property you want and of what will be the size and in which location, etc.\r\n\r\nWe would access our extensive database and immediately find a suitable property for you. We would also help you in negotiating the price and help with other aspects of the transaction. Buying Properties in Andhra Pradesh is easy now! Our services cover various residential, commercial, industrial and agricultural properties.\r\n<h1>Buying a home - step by step guide</h1>\r\n<span class=\"introText\"> Find out the process you need to follow when buying a home, including working out your budget and applying for a mortgage. You can also get help to buy a property, through affordable home ownership schemes.</span>\r\n<h2>A home-buying checklist</h2>\r\nBuying a home typically takes around two to three months and there are a number of steps you will need to take. You need to decide what you’re looking for and where and think about what your needs are - for example:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>where you want to live</li>\r\n	<li>whether you want a flat, a detached, a semi-detached or terraced property</li>\r\n	<li>how many rooms you need and how big they need to be</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Decide on your budget</h2>\r\nThink about what you can afford to spend. You’ll need to budget and plan for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>one-off costs, like a deposit and Stamp Duty</li>\r\n	<li>regular, ongoing costs, like mortgage payments, rates and utilities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor a list of the different costs, see ‘Mortgages and buying property’.\r\n\r\nYou don’t need to make a full mortgage application until you’ve found a property you want to buy.\r\n<h2>Get finances in place</h2>\r\nIf you can’t afford to buy a home without borrowing money, you can apply for a mortgage. Most lenders will give you an idea of how much money they are willing to lend you, called a ‘mortgage or agreement in principle’.\r\n<h2>Find a suitable property</h2>\r\nThere are several ways to find a property. Most people use an estate agent, but you can also buy direct from the seller (a private sale) or at auction.\r\n<h2>Make an offer for the property</h2>\r\nOnce you’ve found a property, you’ll need to make an offer to the seller.\r\n<h2>Hire a solicitor</h2>\r\nYour solicitor will deal directly with those of the vendors or sellers and carries out the legal work involved in buying a property. The estate agent will ask both you and the vendors for details of the solicitors to be used for the buying and selling.\r\n<h2>Get the property surveyed</h2>\r\nOnce your offer is accepted, you should get the property checked for any defects in its condition that might affect the value.\r\n\r\nYour mortgage lender may need a separate valuation to confirm the value of the property.\r\n<h2>Apply for a mortgage</h2>\r\nIf you don’t have the money to buy the property outright, you’ll need to make a full application for a mortgage. You can find more information in the link below:\r\n<h2>Exchange contracts</h2>\r\nThe exchange of the contracts to buy the property is the point where the sale is legally binding.\r\n\r\nSolicitors for both sides will get the buyer and the seller to sign a contract. This says you agree to the terms of the sale and to buy the property. You and the seller must now stick to the terms of the contract or face going to court.\r\n\r\nThe contract will list items that are included in the sale or that you’ve agreed to buy such as electrical items or furniture.\r\n\r\nYou’ll usually need to pay a deposit of 10 per cent of the house price to the seller at this point.\r\n<h2>Pay for the property and move in</h2>\r\nAfter the final legal tasks are complete, your solicitor will arrange for your mortgage company to pay the rest of the money to the seller’s solicitor. When this is done, the house belongs to you and you can move in on the agreed date. This is called ‘completion’.\r\n<h3>Be prepared for unexpected delays</h3>\r\nIf you’re buying a property, you’ll often find yourself in a chain of people, all relying on selling their property to buy a new property. This means the property you want to buy may fall through for reasons outside your control.\r\n\r\nBe prepared to arrange alternative temporary accommodation if you have to move out of your property.\r\n<h2>Get help to buy a home</h2>\r\nHigh property prices have made it difficult for many people to afford to buy a home. There are a number of schemes aimed at helping. You can find out more in the link below:[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Buying Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2015-12-24 12:34:45','2015-12-24 12:34:45','',44,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(366,1,'2015-12-24 12:35:17','2015-12-24 12:35:17','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Construction Services</strong><strong>\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES is entrusted with the key activities involving translation of the physical manifestation of design, meeting all the safety and quality standards within the agreed time schedule of the project. We provide Construction Management Services for various clients in India and abroad at diverse project locations. Our services for total Construction Management of a project include:\r\n\r\nPre-construction activities such as bid management process, constru